  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nBeacon API `v2.4.0` defines a [liveness](https://ethereum.github.io/beacon-APIs/?urls.primaryName=v2.4.0#/Validator/getLiveness) endpoint (in some ways similar to [this]( https://lighthouse-book.sigmaprime.io/api-lighthouse.html#lighthouseliveness)).\r\n\r\nDoes the Lighthouse team plan to implement it?\r\n\r\n**EDIT:** Replace link in \"in some ways similar to\" by the good one.\r\n\r\n",
